Database (RDBMS)
    - Hash(sha512)
    - Timestamp
    - Lifespan
    [- Short ID]
- Server
    - Golang (Sven, Lars)
    - Python3+Flask (Sascha)
    [- Python+Django (Lars)])
- Frontend (Html + JS)
    - AngularJS 2.x (Lars)
    - CryptoJS
- Datei
    - /prefix/Hash
    - Format: <Header>\n\n<Body>
[- Nginx]
        [- Upload Module]

- RESTful/like API
    - GET /
        - Upload UI
    - GET /ui/*
        - Ressources
    - PUT /api/<sha512-hash>[/<lifespan>]
        - X-HTTP-LIFESPAN
        - Returns: JSON
        - 409 Conflict
        - 201 Created
    - GET /api/<sha512-hash>
        - Returns: File
        - 200 OK
        - 404 Not Found
    - GET /<sha512-hash>
        - Download UI
        - 200 OK

Interface:
    - Upload:
        - lifespan (dropdown)
        - password [generator]
        - browse file
        [- shorten (checkbox)]
    - Download
        - Download button
        - Password

